Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環…境省？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  環境省超自然災害對策室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是消除惡靈的國家機關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  土宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭次斬殺的類型D居然是熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點挨不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且並非低等怨靈  而是被魍魎操控的死者的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:02:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然災害源的活動已經平定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的靈氣壓也恢復到了正常值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個特異點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於1950時荒川河岸附近的出現之後反應就消失了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓處理班恢復到通常待機狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測班繼續警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓神樂先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在精神不穩定的情況下進行作戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易引發失誤  更可能會讓同伴陷入危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話真冷談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果措辭委婉能讓事態好轉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有讓事態回轉的好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓諫山黃泉也一同休假如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓土宮神樂覺得只有自己被排擠在任務之外會起到反效果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是她的話相信也能安定神樂的精神狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  小桐你冷談的說法也挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替前幾日在交通事故中去世的保健醫生中林老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的板橋老師上任了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後保健委員好像還有個會議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真鍋  你聽見了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了出席
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長  你找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是把家主傳給黃泉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想提前預定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長…難道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時還死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但話說回來  這年紀了誰也不知道以後會出什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在還能動彈的時候讓她繼承家主  我也好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算在下次的分家會議上  正式把家主之位傳給黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽  希望你能幫我準備一下此事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你聽到的  幫我準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高橋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津村 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮今天也請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新來的板橋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腿怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被玻璃劃破的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓玻璃劃破的  怎麼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打碎了窗戶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不會留下傷痕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心一點  你是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  包紮完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感到繃帶有什麼不適隨時過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會馬上幫你換的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  弄疼你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:08:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你殺的  你又哭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你做的吧  說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說連我都要砍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會砍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是我還是真紅都會砍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那麼喜歡你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也是  土宮也是  明明很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一聲不吭  就算是藉口也行倒是說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你說話你聽沒聽見嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要打…就打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨我的話  隨你怎麼打都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該這樣子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是工作  就算我不想砍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那是我想保護的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我錯了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是我錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  你們怨我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍我好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  冥姐  你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找爸爸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  事情已經談完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近挺活躍的嘛  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢  獅子丸可是在你手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不做出點成績來可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:11:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諫山家代代相傳的寶刀  原本可不是你等外道能夠使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要謹記這其中的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  土宮就是退魔師一族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總有一天也要成為獨當一面的退魔師而繼承靈獸才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白叡  那是土宮家相傳的最強靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要維持那個封印  將靈魂與其相連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是生為土宮家人的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說土宮經常請假  看到簡訊就早退是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  這是生為土宮家人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不可思議了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有家人會讓小孩子去做那種危險的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是家傳的使命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那更奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就非要土宮來繼承啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…就是這種宿命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就奇怪到天邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說使命啊宿命啊什麼的太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說土宮你一定要做的話我也不會反對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  土宮你是真想繼承那樣的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈力分佈觀測班傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是那個特異點又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…特異點有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大的那個比起以前靈力場規模有所縮小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說分裂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  的確有這可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實戰的話你可就死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同歸於盡也是輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想什麼捨身戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想無傷退敵的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  進步挺大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我學會剛才那招反擊方式可是花了不少時間的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…這樣繼續下去真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始我並不太明白工作是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看到黃泉驅使靈獸而很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得退治惡靈保護大家是件很帥的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以努力奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以放棄離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過做決定的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在就盡情煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管別人說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要最後你找到自己心中的那個答案就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少我是這麼一路走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼樣的答案  只要是神樂你自己決定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都站在你這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都站在你這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的那個朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說她請客讓我趕快過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  挺好的朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她理解你了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠了  好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也算放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂變得精神一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子成天到晚都在說神樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  她和我很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被惡靈殺死家人  背負著退魔師的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓她承受和我一樣的痛苦回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想就這麼一直保護著她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…差不多也到頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂也許已經用不著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她啊  一瞬間就把我花了數年才掌握的招式學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久她就會超過我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素質真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是身世好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承最強靈獸的土宮家的嫡子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔師中也算是屈指可數的家族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及與生俱來的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有著我如何渴望也得不到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她卻在煩惱著是否要繼承這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了繼承諫山家業也付出了不少努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有了就算在退魔師中也是數一數二的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長到今天被人稱作神童的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣  還是有人覺得我並不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有人可以責難你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬頭挺胸走下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你壞話的人  我是不會放過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得最多的不是紀之你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪張嘴…說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  我現在和小千她們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛  還順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說是請我  但輸了撲克牌變成我請她們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來黃泉  今天晚飯準備如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就吃神樂喜歡吃的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉你決定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我想吃蔬菜咖喱汪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.76,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點冰淇淋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂你難道不餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我忘記正在進行少量減肥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用邊角砸我啦  邊角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再敢這樣小心我咬掉你的舌頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今天的任務已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來囉～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃咖喱哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔？叔叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  回來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂你怎麼待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他…叔叔他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔！這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  這時候你跑到哪裡玩去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本聯絡不到  一直在找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  首先請和令尊道別
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:26.36,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:37.04,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:47.76,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.75,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:23:00.35,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.75,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:11.02,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:26.51,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:26.36,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經對自己的心靈　許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:37.04,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救贖　捲入嘆息漩渦中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:47.76,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的時光轉瞬即逝　道理的齒輪鏽跡斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:52.75,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已經無法後退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:23:00.35,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毀一切　亦無容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.75,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:11.02,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將那時僅有的幸福　深情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:26.51,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}將遠去的夢的足音　刻骨銘心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  喰靈  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「復仇之路」


